# Window Operations Menus
DestroyMenu MenuWindowOps
AddToMenu   MenuWindowOps
+ "Move"                Move
+ "Resize"              Resize
+ "(De)Iconify"         Thumbnail
+ "(Un)Maximize"        Maximize
+ "Snap Left"           ResizeMoveMaximize frame 50wa 100wa 0 0
+ "Snap Right"          ResizeMoveMaximize frame 50wa 100wa -0 0
+ ""                    Nop
+ "(Un)Shade"           WindowShade
+ "(Un)Sticky"          Stick
+ "(No)TitleBar"        Pick (CirculateHit) ToggleTitle
+ "Stick to Desk"       StickAcrossPages
+ "Stick to Page"       StickAcrossDesks
+ ""                    Nop
+ "Send To"             Popup MenuSendTo
+ ""                    Nop
+ "Raise"               Raise
+ "Lower"               Lower
+ "StaysOnTop"          Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 6
+ "StaysPut"            Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 4
+ "StaysOnBottom"       Pick (CirculateHit) Layer 0 2
+ ""                    Nop
+ "Identify"            Module FvwmIdent
+ "Close"               Close
+ "Destroy"             Destroy

DestroyFunc ToggleTitle
AddToFunc   ToggleTitle
+ I ThisWindow (State 1) WindowStyle Title
+ I TestRc (Match) State 1 False
+ I TestRc (Match) Break
+ I WindowStyle !Title
+ I State 1 True

DestroyFunc MoveToCurrent
AddToFunc MoveToCurrent
+ I ThisWindow MoveToPage
+ I ThisWindow MoveToDesk

DestroyMenu MenuSendTo
AddToMenu MenuSendTo
+ "Current" MoveToCurrent
+ "Page" PopUp MenuSendToPage
+ "Desk" PopUp MenuSendToDesk

DestroyMenu MenuSendToDesk
AddToMenu   MenuSendToDesk
+ $[infostore.desktopname0] MoveToDesk 0 0
+ $[infostore.desktopname1] MoveToDesk 0 1
+ $[infostore.desktopname2] MoveToDesk 0 2

DestroyMenu MenuSendToPage
AddToMenu   MenuSendToPage
+ "1"	MoveToPage 0 0
+ "2"	MoveToPage 0 1
+ "3"	MoveToPage 0 2
+ "4"	MoveToPage 0 3

################################# Keybindings #################################

# Ignore Numlock and other modifiers for bindings
# See http://fvwm.org/documentation/faq/#why-do-numlock-capslock-and-scrolllock-interfere-with-clicktofocus-andor-my-mouse-bindings
IgnoreModifiers L25

Key space A 4 Menu MenuFvwmRoot
Key Tab A 4 WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Super_L, CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd
Key Tab A 1 WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Alt_L, CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd
Key F4 A N WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease F4, CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd
Key 1 A 4 GotoDesk 0 0
Key 2 A 4 GotoDesk 0 1
Key 3 A 4 GotoDesk 0 2
Key 1 A S4 MovetoDesk 0 0
Key 2 A S4 MovetoDesk 0 1
Key 3 A S4 MovetoDesk 0 2
Key w A 4 GotoPage wrapy 0p -1p
Key a A 4 GotoDesk -1
Key s A 4 GotoPage wrapy 0p +1p
Key d A 4 GotoDesk +1
Key w A S4 MovetoPage 0p -1p
Key a A S4 MovetoDesk -1
Key s A S4 MovetoPage 0p +1p
Key d A S4 MovetoDesk +1
Key Left A 4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 50wa 100wa 0 0
Key Right A 4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 50wa 100wa -0 0
Key Up A 4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 100wa 50wa 0 0
Key Down A 4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 100wa 50wa 0 -0
Key Insert A 4 ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa 0 0
Key End A 4 ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa -0 -0
Key Home A 4  ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa -0 0
Key Delete A 4 ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa 0 -0
Key f A 4 Maximize Fullscreen
Key 0 A 4 Thumbnail
Key m A 4 ResizeMove frame 75wa 85wa 260p 100p
Key 7 A 4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 59wa 100wa 0 0
Key 8 A 4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 40wa 59wa -0 0
Key 9 A 4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 40wa 39wa -0 -0
Key Return A 4 Exec exec $[TERMINAL]
Silent Key XF86AudioRaiseVolume A N Exec amixer sset Master unmute && exec amixer sset Master 5%+
Silent Key XF86AudioLowerVolume A N Exec amixer sset Master unmute && exec amixer sset Master 5%-
Silent Key XF86AudioMute A N Exec exec amixer sset Master mute
Silent Key KP_Add A 4 Exec amixer sset Master unmute && exec amixer sset Master 5%+
Silent Key KP_Subtract A 4 Exec amixer sset Master unmute && exec amixer sset Master 5%-
Silent Key KP_Insert A 4 Exec exec amixer sset Master mute
Silent Key XF86MonBrightnessDown A N Exec exec xbacklight -dec 10
Silent Key XF86MonBrightnessUp A N Exec exec xbacklight -inc 10
Silent Key XF86AudioPlay A N Exec exec strawberry --play-pause
Silent Key XF86AudioPrev A N Exec exec strawberry --restart-or-previous
Silent Key XF86AudioNext A N Exec exec strawberry --next
Silent Key KP_End A 4 Exec exec strawberry --play-pause
Silent Key KP_Divide A 4 Exec exec strawberry --restart-or-previous
Silent Key KP_Multiply A 4 Exec exec strawberry --next

